name: Miss Algorithm #Every_curl_a_Whim #25/30
description:
We browse conditioned by persuasive proposals because the "Algorithm Family" exists within our computers and mobile phones. Ladies and gentlemen, not too old with a formidable memory, they have their own life and grow together with our clicks.

Each of them remembers where we would like to go on vacation, which stylist we prefer or how we would like to feed ourselves, they know a lot about us and often influence our choices.

I had a lot of fun creating portraits, each linked to the algorithm of a #hashtag.

This is the portrait of Miss Algorithm #Every_curl_a_Whim

File size: 2.000 x 2784 px - 200 dpi

limited series n. 30 copies

serial number: #25
